Title: Anton Bruckner - Symphony no. 4 First version: Daniel Harding conducting the LSO in 2008
Description:
Daniel Harding conducting the first (1874) version of Bruckner's fourth symphony, with the London Symphony Orchestra at the Barbican in October 2008.


1. Allegro 0:00
2. Andante, quasi allegretto 20:25
3. Sehr schnell - Trio - Im gleich 40:23
4. Allegro moderato 54:30
